WEBVTT

00:00:14.725 --> 00:00:18.487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

00:00:18.562 --> 00:00:22.162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

00:00:22.287 --> 00:00:25.437
♪Your "same here" carries
a touch of resolve♪

00:00:25.862 --> 00:00:29.412
♪Pack my bags, we can set off right now♪

00:00:29.637 --> 00:00:33.112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

00:00:33.250 --> 00:00:36.712
♪The journey itself is what
truly matters before the destination♪

00:00:36.787 --> 00:00:40.975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

00:00:41.025 --> 00:00:42.612
♪Connect♪

00:00:42.625 --> 00:00:43.275
♪Let's go!♪

00:00:43.612 --> 00:00:47.137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

00:00:47.237 --> 00:00:50.675
♪Today, no dwelling
on negative emotions♪

00:00:50.750 --> 00:00:53.450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

00:00:53.450 --> 00:00:55.262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

00:00:55.262 --> 00:00:58.199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

00:00:59.075 --> 00:01:02.375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

00:01:02.675 --> 00:01:06.262
=Episode 14=

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:09.520
I'm so sorry, Zhu.

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:10.320
I've dragged you

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:12.360
into all of this mess with me.

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:14.000
It's okay.

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.390
It's not like you wanted this.

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:17.840
I guess we've been
through life and death together now.

00:01:18.760 --> 00:01:19.640
I guess so.

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:22.240
But I always get the feeling

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:23.360
that your brother...

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:24.160
Ze.

00:01:27.160 --> 00:01:29.360
Are you really going
to Singapore with me?

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:30.800
What's there to doubt?

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:32.040
Don't you know?

00:01:32.080 --> 00:01:34.280
My greatest dream is...

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:38.960
As long as I'm with you,

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:40.040
I'm willing to go anywhere.

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:41.960
Oh, right.

00:01:42.120 --> 00:01:43.840
Did you make a wish last night?

00:01:44.240 --> 00:01:44.600
Huh?

00:01:45.240 --> 00:01:46.160
What wish?

00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:47.960
There were shooting stars last night.

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:49.480
I knew you didn't.

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:50.600
I already made one for you.

00:01:52.240 --> 00:01:53.440
What did you wish for me?

00:01:55.920 --> 00:01:56.760
It's a secret.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:58.440
Tianze.

00:01:59.680 --> 00:02:00.760
My dad is calling me.

00:02:01.000 --> 00:02:01.920
I'm heading back now.

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:26.920
(Can my wish)

00:02:27.720 --> 00:02:29.160
(still come true?)

00:02:57.262 --> 00:02:57.895
Zhu.

00:03:01.725 --> 00:03:02.287
Look at this.

00:03:03.350 --> 00:03:04.012
Here.

00:03:12.537 --> 00:03:13.312
What does this mean?

00:03:14.812 --> 00:03:16.387
Situation. "Qing kuang."

00:03:16.512 --> 00:03:19.825
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:03:20.312 --> 00:03:24.187
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:03:24.537 --> 00:03:28.380
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:03:28.380 --> 00:03:32.060
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:03:32.060 --> 00:03:35.860
♪I'll learn to stop longing
for what's gone♪

00:03:35.860 --> 00:03:37.820
♪The you in my memories♪

00:03:41.880 --> 00:03:42.680
Everyone.

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:46.280
Our project

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:49.120
is a success!

00:04:09.490 --> 00:04:10.880
This project still needs follow-up.

00:04:10.900 --> 00:04:12.000
Understood. See you, Mr. Ye.

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:12.680
Man.

00:04:15.300 --> 00:04:16.520
I have something to say to you.

00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:18.680
What is it?

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:21.240
Our victory this time

00:04:21.850 --> 00:04:22.920
wasn't because our project

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:24.760
was so visionary or marketable.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:27.320
Then, what was it?

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:31.090
It depended on
whether the president of the Lu Group

00:04:31.240 --> 00:04:34.120
was willing to use his veto power

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:35.280
somewhere else or not.

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:37.400
What do you mean?

00:04:39.300 --> 00:04:41.160
You and I are people
who need to move forward.

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:43.680
But if someone
stands in the way of our progress,

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:46.240
we should find a way
around them without hesitation.

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:48.720
So,

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:52.560
I was a stumbling block
on your road to success,

00:04:53.190 --> 00:04:55.120
and you chose
to kick me aside effortlessly,

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:55.880
right?

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:57.880
Lily.

00:05:00.120 --> 00:05:01.480
I really admire your talent.

00:05:04.550 --> 00:05:05.990
And I really did love you.

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:09.920
However,

00:05:10.760 --> 00:05:12.440
I realized we are not on the same path.

00:05:16.520 --> 00:05:17.720
Good work, Miss Fan.

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:28.880
Man.

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:31.320
Man.

00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:46.120
I missed you.

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:47.120
Me too.

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:49.480
Sit down.

00:05:53.112 --> 00:05:53.950
What's wrong?

00:05:54.010 --> 00:05:55.412
What were you just thinking about?

00:05:56.775 --> 00:05:59.695
Do you know what
"conflicting interests" means?

00:06:04.160 --> 00:06:06.000
For anything in this world,

00:06:06.737 --> 00:06:08.162
once it's tied to profit,

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:10.420
its core essence changes.

00:06:11.275 --> 00:06:12.555
You either go with the flow,

00:06:13.575 --> 00:06:14.735
or you fight against it.

00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:20.760
Why am I telling you all this?

00:06:20.760 --> 00:06:21.700
You wouldn't understand.

00:06:22.680 --> 00:06:23.480
I do.

00:06:26.080 --> 00:06:27.720
But I won't just go with the flow,

00:06:28.440 --> 00:06:29.800
nor will I fight against it.

00:06:33.500 --> 00:06:34.550
Then, what would you do?

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:37.080
Right or wrong,

00:06:37.687 --> 00:06:39.007
I will always choose you.

00:06:40.480 --> 00:06:41.520
Unwaveringly.

00:06:44.125 --> 00:06:45.500
It has nothing to do with profit,

00:06:46.370 --> 00:06:48.055
nor does it matter
if interests conflict.

00:06:50.150 --> 00:06:51.030
As long as it's you.

00:06:55.280 --> 00:06:56.480
Right or wrong, it's you.

00:07:13.920 --> 00:07:15.720
Welcome to my studio.

00:07:23.280 --> 00:07:24.680
Why did you paint this?

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.342
I don't know why,

00:07:31.440 --> 00:07:33.160
but every time I see the ocean,

00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:35.280
I don't feel afraid.

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:37.040
Instead, I feel safe.

00:07:39.480 --> 00:07:40.800
The darkness of the seabed

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:42.800
makes me want to keep exploring.

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:47.080
Especially after I met you.

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:50.600
You constantly stand
in front of me to protect me,

00:07:51.650 --> 00:07:53.975
making the hope
I hid in the depths come true.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.160
Do you like it?

00:08:04.012 --> 00:08:04.700
Yes.

00:08:06.462 --> 00:08:07.342
What do you like?

00:08:14.760 --> 00:08:16.040
I like you.

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:31.960
I'll take this call.

00:08:37.880 --> 00:08:40.360
(While you're alive,
live to the fullest.)

00:08:40.360 --> 00:08:41.720
(Love others with all you have.)

00:08:41.720 --> 00:08:43.200
(Try your best to be loved.)

00:08:43.200 --> 00:08:44.840
(That way, when death comes,)

00:08:44.840 --> 00:08:47.920
(you won't be reluctant
or afraid anymore.)

00:08:57.160 --> 00:08:58.200
In three months,

00:08:58.200 --> 00:09:00.000
we won't give you any more chances.

00:09:00.160 --> 00:09:01.520
We can forget about the money,

00:09:01.520 --> 00:09:04.760
but we will definitely
expose what Ye Liang did.

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:07.480
He shouldn't think
that death ends everything.

00:09:07.480 --> 00:09:10.000
We'll find a way
to make his name stink forever.

00:09:22.280 --> 00:09:23.320
What's going on?

00:09:24.880 --> 00:09:26.440
Qingbai, look at this.

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:28.400
This...

00:09:31.960 --> 00:09:33.160
You two, look.

00:09:33.160 --> 00:09:34.440
Is this you?

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:36.680
(He's Ye Man, the son of the Ye Group)
Is this you?

00:09:37.720 --> 00:09:38.960
Are you satisfied now?

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:40.840
Once this news got out,

00:09:40.840 --> 00:09:42.160
it spread everywhere.

00:09:42.160 --> 00:09:44.000
The impact on the group is too much.

00:09:44.000 --> 00:09:45.160
Don't you know?

00:09:45.720 --> 00:09:47.120
You're siblings, you know that?

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:48.920
Siblings, do you understand?

00:09:49.440 --> 00:09:51.120
What are you doing?

00:09:51.920 --> 00:09:53.560
Ridiculous!

00:09:53.712 --> 00:09:55.487
You'd better behave yourselves.

00:10:01.137 --> 00:10:01.937
Mom,

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:05.000
this has nothing to do with Lu.

00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:07.400
And you!

00:10:09.040 --> 00:10:10.600
You've really disappointed me.

00:10:10.840 --> 00:10:12.360
What are you acting for?

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:15.240
Didn't you know about this long ago?

00:10:15.840 --> 00:10:17.920
Weren't you the one
who leaked these photos?

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:20.360
Only you

00:10:20.360 --> 00:10:21.600
would do something like this.

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:22.000
Lu.

00:10:23.880 --> 00:10:24.680
Man.

00:10:33.720 --> 00:10:36.520
I have been doing my best
to pave the way for you.

00:10:36.840 --> 00:10:38.160
You've offended Mr. Lu.

00:10:38.720 --> 00:10:39.960
How will your future be?

00:10:40.087 --> 00:10:41.720
Why can't we be together?

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:43.360
Are we related by blood?

00:10:43.360 --> 00:10:45.720
I'm already married to Mr. Lu.

00:10:45.880 --> 00:10:47.760
Can there be a future for you and her?

00:10:47.760 --> 00:10:49.360
Would Mr. Lu ever agree to this?

00:10:55.787 --> 00:10:56.850
Think about it carefully.

00:11:07.240 --> 00:11:08.920
Hey, look. Is that her on the phone?

00:11:31.820 --> 00:11:33.240
I used to only hear
about female gold diggers.

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:34.760
Now, there are male ones too.

00:11:34.760 --> 00:11:35.840
Isn't it her they're talking about?

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:37.600
Yes, it's her.

00:11:38.600 --> 00:11:40.440
Hey, isn't this her?

00:11:47.850 --> 00:11:52.350
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

00:11:52.575 --> 00:11:56.363
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

00:11:56.538 --> 00:12:00.613
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

00:12:00.613 --> 00:12:04.750
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

00:12:04.875 --> 00:12:08.650
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

00:12:08.650 --> 00:12:12.425
♪I'll learn to stop longing
for what's gone♪

00:12:12.425 --> 00:12:14.700
♪The you in my memories♪

00:12:14.700 --> 00:12:16.713
♪Will fade from clarity♪

00:12:16.713 --> 00:12:22.150
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

00:12:23.713 --> 00:12:29.150
♪Forget you completely♪